WEBVTT

00:04:31.920 --> 00:04:34.520
S druge strane je bila tišina.

00:04:35.160 --> 00:04:36.890
A onda je rekao:

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:40.120
„Moram da pitam suprugu.“

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:41.518
(Smeh)

00:04:41.518 --> 00:04:42.654
Šta?

00:04:42.764 --> 00:04:44.200
Rasista ima suprugu?

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:45.566
(Smeh)

00:04:46.076 --> 00:04:48.986
Par dana kasnije sreli smo se kod njega.

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:53.440
Nikada neću zaboraviti
kada je otvorio vrata

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:55.633
i pružio mi ruku.

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:58.920
Bila sam razočarana.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:00.146
(Smeh)